#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.wald.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.wald"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a Wald, or inverse Gaussian, distribution."
msgstr "从 Wald 分布（或逆高斯分布）中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:3 of
msgid ""
"As the scale approaches infinity, the distribution becomes more like a "
"Gaussian. Some references claim that the Wald is an inverse Gaussian with"
" mean equal to 1, but this is by no means universal."
msgstr ""
"当 scale 趋近于无穷大时，该分布越来越接近高斯分布。一些文献认为 Wald 分布"
"是均值为 1 的逆高斯分布，但这并不具有普遍性。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:7 of
msgid ""
"The inverse Gaussian distribution was first studied in relationship to "
"Brownian motion. In 1956 M.C.K. Tweedie used the name inverse Gaussian "
"because there is an inverse relationship between the time to cover a unit"
" distance and distance covered in unit time."
msgstr ""
"逆高斯分布最初是在研究布朗运动时被引入的。1956 年，M.C.K. Tweedie 使用“"
"逆高斯”这一名称，因为单位距离所需时间和单位时间内所走距离之间存在反比"
"关系。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:12 of
msgid "Distribution mean, should be > 0."
msgstr "分布的均值，应大于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:14 of
msgid "Scale parameter, should be >= 0."
msgstr "尺度参数，应大于等于 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:16 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``mean`` and ``scale`` are both scalars. Otherwise, "
"``np.broadcast(mean, scale).size`` samples are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状为 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。如果"
" size 为 ``None``（默认），且 ``mean`` 和 ``scale`` 均为标量，则返回单个"
"值。否则，抽取 ``np.broadcast(mean, scale).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:21 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的分块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:23 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则将张量分配在 GPU 上，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:25 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:28 of
msgid "**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized Wald distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的 Wald 分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:32 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:33 of
msgid "The probability density function for the Wald distribution is"
msgstr "Wald 分布的概率密度函数为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:35 of
msgid ""
"P(x;mean,scale) = \\sqrt{\\frac{scale}{2\\pi x^3}}e^\n"
"\\frac{-scale(x-mean)^2}{2\\cdotp mean^2x}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:38 of
msgid ""
"As noted above the inverse Gaussian distribution first arise from "
"attempts to model Brownian motion. It is also a competitor to the Weibull"
" for use in reliability modeling and modeling stock returns and interest "
"rate processes."
msgstr ""
"如上所述，逆高斯分布最初源于对布朗运动的建模尝试。它也是 Weibull 分布在"
"可靠性建模以及股票收益和利率过程建模中的竞争模型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:44 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:45 of
msgid ""
"Brighton Webs Ltd., Wald Distribution, http://www.brighton-"
"webs.co.uk/distributions/wald.asp"
msgstr ""
"Brighton Webs Ltd., Wald 分布, http://www.brighton-webs.co.uk/"
"distributions/wald.asp"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:47 of
msgid ""
"Chhikara, Raj S., and Folks, J. Leroy, \"The Inverse Gaussian "
"Distribution: Theory : Methodology, and Applications\", CRC Press, 1988."
msgstr ""
"Chhikara, Raj S., 和 Folks, J. Leroy, 《逆高斯分布：理论、方法与应用》, "
"CRC Press, 1988."

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:50 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Wald distribution\" "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wald_distribution"
msgstr "Wikipedia, \"Wald 分布\" http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wald_distribution"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.wald.wald:54 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

